title: The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild[WiiU] 1080p Cutscene
description:
Cut-scenes extracted and re-encoded from Nintendo Switch version. For use with BotW WiiU on Cemu. Requires CemuHook 0.5.3.2 or later to work.

How to install:
1. Back up the "contentMovies" directory in your BotW game folder
2. Replace "contentMovies" with ones provided
